Freeze your foes with fear when you play the Frost Ray theme deck! Use Glaceon's Icy Wind attack to send opposing Pokmon into a cold, deep sleep, and Vanilluxe's powerful ChillMAX attack to let them know they're in for a rude awakening! You'll command the battlefield with superior speed using Glaceon's Freeze Zone Ability, and help keep the Energy flowing with Electrode's Magnetic Draw. Then, as you call Team Plasma Pokmon and Trainer cards from the discard pile with Raticate's Transfer Junk attack, your opponents will know anyone unwary enough to challenge you will be put on ice!

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

results.cleanName: Plasma Freeze Theme Deck Psy Crusher Leafeon

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Mash your opponents' minds with mental might when you play the Psy Crusher theme deck! Use Leafeon's Energy Crush attack to turn the power of opposing Pokmon on themselves, and make sure no Pokmon can escape when you unleash Cofagrigus's Elongating Arms attack! Espeon keeps the reinforcements coming with Psy Alert, and Muk deals damage and heals itself. Then, when Beedrill Confuses and Poisons using Swift Sting, it won't take a mind-reader to know that the shattered remnants of the forces facing you have been crushed!

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin
